<h4 id="doc-notes">Notes</h4>
<ul>
<li>Combine <code>.transition-rotate</code> with
<code>.duration-*</code> for smooth rotation.</li>
<li>Use <code>.transition</code> if multiple CSS properties (e.g.,
color, box-shadow) should animate together.</li>
<li>Ensure elements with transforms do not interfere with layout (e.g.,
overlapping or scaling out of bounds).</li>
</ul>
